籤詩版本二:
Nokuba ungawucima umlilo ngeenkuni, kuya kutsha yonke into, nokuba uthe wavutha amaxesha angamawaka amathathu, kuya kwenzeka kwakhona.
Ukuba unenkxalabo malunga nozuko kunye nobutyebi, kungcono ukucoca umzamo ochithekileyo
詩意:
Le hexagram ifana nokubamba iinkuni ukucima umlilo.
Lumka kuyo yonke into.
解曰: Kukho amawaka ezicwangciso. Wakhe wacatshukiswa. Kungcono ungahambi. Ukoyika ukwenza inkathazo.
籤詩故事一:
◇Idabi laseChibi
Ngexesha loBukumkani obuThathu, umkhosi kaCao Cao wawumi kunxweme lwaseChibi.
Injengele yeSun Quan uZhou Yu wadibanisa umkhosi kaLiu Bei ngokuchasene noCao Cao.
I-Kongming yathatha ithuba lomoya wasempumalanga, kwaye u-Huang Gai watshisa umlilo kwinqanawa yekhonkco, kwaye imikhosi emibini yalwa ngokukrakra.
Kwakukho ulwandle lomlilo, kwaye umkhosi kaCao woyiswa. Ngokwembali yayisaziwa njengeDabi laseChibi.
